description: Welcome to this impressive condo offering 2 bedrooms & 1 bath, loaded with major must-haves! Enjoy the convenience of parking & the luxury of 3 outdoor spaces, including an exclusive 382SF backyard & a massive 400 SF storage room perfect for a home gym, workshop, or any creative endeavor. Step inside to a functional layout featuring a large living room with custom built-ins & a designated dining space that opens through sliders to a delightful, sun-splashed deck—perfect for morning coffee. The well-appointed kitchen boasts custom cabinets, granite counters, SS appliances, & trendy lighting throughout. Both beds offer ample space & double closets. Additional highlights include abundant natural light, central AC, in-unit W/D, HW floors throughout, & excellent ceiling height. Located near developing Washington Village, enjoy amenities like Tatte, Castle Island Brewery, & Red Line T stations for city connectivity. Explore nearby restaurants/shops & all that South Boston has to offer!
